    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "幻影的另一面　前篇",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "“幽影”——\\n那是一头丑陋之龙的名字。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "“幽影”——\\n那是一个人与龙皆忌讳的存在。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "利爪、尖牙以及漆黑的躯体，\\n其样貌宛如魔兽。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": "BOOK_210045_01"
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "尽管相貌丑陋，\\n其内心却如犹如清泉般\\n充满了“仁慈”。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "但无人愿意去看、去注意、去思考。\\n啊，多么残酷。\\n他们一口咬定\\n“外表丑陋的东西，内心也一定丑恶”。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "幽影踏上了旅途，\\n只求一丝喘息。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "他来到了一个\\n被魔兽蹂躏的国度。\\n他那纯洁的心灵，\\n令他对那些逃亡的人们心生怜悯。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": "BOOK_120007_01"
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "幽影投入到战斗之中。\\n即使国破家亡，\\n也要保住人们的性命。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "恐怖的魔兽终于被打倒，\\n人们的性命保住了。\\n正当他松了一口气时……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "“你这该死的魔兽！”\\n“毁了我们国家的就是你吗！”\\n他得到的不是感谢，\\n而是无数骑士的剑。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "“不！不是我！”“该死的魔兽！”\\n“我是龙啊！”“你是魔兽！”\\n“我……”“不！不！不！”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "“你这丑陋的魔兽……\\n不，灾难的元凶！”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "自那以后，\\n他便被人们称为“幽影”。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "既然丑恶之物永无安宁，\\n又为何要拥有永恒的生命？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "幽影消失了。\\n他被人们咒骂着，\\n远离了这个世界。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "记忆是脆弱的。\\n如今已无人记得\\n那头被封印的龙。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "“幽影”——\\n他早已不再是龙。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "如今……只是一抹幻影……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}